name: Whole30

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: whole thirty
des:
The Whole30 is a 30-day diet that emphasizes consuming whole foods and eliminating sugars, alcohol, grains, legumes, soy, and dairy from your diet.

Sometimes it can be confusing whether or not a food or drink is safe to consume on the Whole30 diet. Now you can find out! Simply ask Whole30 if an item is ok to eat and Alexa will let you know.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
